class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Dez 12, 2022</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104otq1665702997846.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/otq1665702997846.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/otq1665702997846.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"otq1665702997846\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\"> Migration to Uniface 10.4 \n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body taskbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">How to migrate to Uniface 10.4</p>\n<section class=\"section context\" id=\"otq1665702997846__context_w2770ab1b5b1_w2771ab1b5_w2772ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"otq1665702997846__p_d68291e1_d68292e1_d68293e1\">When you install Uniface <span class=\"ph\">10.4</span>, it creates a new Repository. It is not possible to run the Uniface 10 IDE (or later) against an older Repository, such as Uniface 10.3 or Uniface 9. You must therefore migrate your existing sources to the new Repository.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"otq1665702997846__p_d68294e1_d68295e1_d68296e1\">Whether you are migrating from Uniface 9, the Uniface 10.3 Enterprise Edition, or the Uniface Community Edition, the basic migration steps are the same:</p>\n</section>\n<section><ol class=\"ol steps\"><li class=\"li step\" id=\"otq1665702997846__li_d30998e1_d30999e1_d31000e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Export your application definitions from your existing Uniface installation.\n </span>\n</li><li class=\"li step\" id=\"otq1665702997846__li_d31001e1_d31002e1_d31003e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Import the definitions into the new Repository. Uniface detects that the definitions must be migrated and starts the Migration Utility which converts the existing definitions to match the new Repository requirements.\n </span>\n</li><li class=\"li step\" id=\"otq1665702997846__li_d31004e1_d31005e1_d31006e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">If you have customized your development and test environment, you will need to configure Uniface <span class=\"ph\">10.4</span> so that it can access the needed database and file resources, and servers.\n </span>\n</li><li class=\"li step\" id=\"otq1665702997846__li_d31007e1_d31008e1_d31009e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Compile and test the migrated application.\n </span>\n</li></ol></section>\n<section class=\"section result body required-cleanup-multiple-ol-elements-in-topic-body\" id=\"otq1665702997846__result_w2773ab1b5b5_w2774ab1b5_w2775ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"otq1665702997846__p_d68297e1_d68298e1_d68299e1\">Depending on the version you are migrating from and the size and complexity of your application and development environment configuration, more work may be required.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530728\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530728\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Migration to Uniface 10.4 Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Dez 12, 2022 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Migration to Uniface 10.4 How to migrate to Uniface 10.4 When you install Uniface 10.4 , it creates a new Repository. It is not possible to run the Uniface 10 IDE (or later) against an older Repository, such as Uniface 10.3 or Uniface 9. You must therefore migrate your existing sources to the new Repository. Whether you are migrating from Uniface 9, the Uniface 10.3 Enterprise Edition, or the Uniface Community Edition, the basic migration steps are the same: Export your application definitions from your existing Uniface installation. Import the definitions into the new Repository. Uniface detects that the definitions must be migrated and starts the Migration Utility which converts the existing definitions to match the new Repository requirements. If you have customized your development and test environment, you will need to configure Uniface 10.4 so that it can access the needed database and file resources, and servers. Compile and test the migrated application. Depending on the version you are migrating from and the size and complexity of your application and development environment configuration, more work may be required. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}